By charging at the EVR, drivers acknowledge that energy consumption patterns, time logged, battery discharge, SOC, and other relevant metrics may be used for confidential electric vehicle research and testing.  **Charging ports may be taken offline during specific intervals according to renewable energy storage capacity, lab testing, and professional conferences.
